  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Amplifying voices - U-Report (SLB-0047)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This initiative encourages young people in Solomon Islandsto participate in U-Report, a digital platform where they can express their voice on the issues that are affecting them through SMS and Facebook Messenger. Issues to be covered include health, nutrition, water, sanitation and hygiene, education, child marriage, violence against children, child online protection, entrepreneurship, SDGs, climate action and so on.  U-Report will complement the &apos;Oxfam Solomon Islands Social Accountability and Youth and Governance Program&apos; by providing a platform for young people to raise issues of concernand find solutions and information in a channel that is readily availablefor them.</narrative>
  </description>
